**Top risks**

1. PDF invoice parsing quality on scanned documents — mitigation: use text-layer extraction first, fallback to Gemini vision
2. German CSV format gotchas causing silent join failures — mitigation: defensive parser with explicit format flags, tested on day-01 delta before building anything else
3. ADK + Entiure integration time cost — mitigation: ADK session state can substitute for Entiure in extremis; Entiure is the upgrade path, not the foundation

